title: Serious accident closes A35 in Dorset | Country (W)
text:
Highways England @HighwaysSWEST Follow #A35 #Dorset remains closed both ways for @ dorestpolice to deal with an accident inv: a car and a lorry. http://t.co/DPn5ooDPkO
05:40 - 4 Aug 2015 Retweet Reply Favourite The A35 is shut in both directions in Bridport following a collision between a car and a lorry.
It happened just after 5am in Sea Road South.
The road is expected to be shut for most of the morning.
Traffic is being diverted via a local route using the B3162 through Bridport.
